                    "description": "you will receive one of four treatment conditions that include active and sham tACS. The four conditions are the following: (1) closed-loop-tACS (peak-locked), (2) closed-loop-tACS (trough-locked), (3) open-loop tACS, and (4) sham tACS. Although each subject will undergo all four treatments in four separate study visits, the order of the treatments will be randomized",
